See INSTALL for installation instructions.

Use like so:

$ nosetests --with-achievements


Using Django? Put this in settings.py:

TEST_RUNNER = 'noseachievements.djangotest.DjangoTestSuiteRunner'


See the list of achievements at: http://exogen.github.com/nose-achievements/


Wanna enable them by default? Use this setup.cfg:

[nosetests]
with-achievements=1

